    footnote: "Sample artifacts. Real datasheets, API references, and SOC 2 control narratives carry deeper structure (datasheets often run 20–40 pages; API specs auto-generated from source typically span hundreds of endpoints; SOC 2 reports cover 50+ Trust Services Criteria) — but the typographic registers shown above are the genuine shapes of these three documentation surfaces.",
