      body: "Single-source DITA across chip families with conditional content for package-variant and grade-level differences. Publishing pipeline integrated with the EDA toolchain so reference-design files and datasheets stay version-aligned. Translation handled across the global engineering markets where the chips ship; a single datasheet now produces compliant outputs for every regional market in one publishing run.",
